But if you stick with the series you get used to it and you're greeted to an absolutely amazing story with loads of plot twists and turns. \
The setting of the show is the 1930s, so obviously there's going to be loads of stories to do with gangs, mafias, crime lords, all that good stuff. But it also gets into stuff WAY more complicated than that like immortality, insanity and even love. Overall, it's a great story that really gets you hooked as long as you stick with it.\
